      <para id="id1167244298365"><emphasis effect="bold">LEARNING OUTCOME 3: </emphasis><emphasis effect="bold">READING AND VIEWING</emphasis>The learner is able to read and view for information and enjoyment, and to respond critically to the aesthetic, cultural and emotional values in texts.<emphasis effect="bold"/></para>
